<h3>NIGHT TIME</h3>

<p>You are <%= @player.display_name %>, a <%= Player::ROLES[@player.role] %></p>

<% if @eliminated_player %>
  <p>The villagers voted to eliminated <%= @eliminated_player.display_name %>. This player was a <%= Player::ROLES[@eliminated_player.role] %></p>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:VILLAGER] %>
  <p>Your goal as a villager is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have no actions to take. Day will begin when the following nighttime actions have completed:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Overnight the Mafiosi are planning which villager to attack.</li>
    <% if @game.use_detective %>
      <li>The detective will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked the detective will learn the identity of the killers.</li>
    <% end %>
    <% if @game.use_doctor %>
      <li>The doctor will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked that villager will survive the attack.</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:MAFIOSO] %>
  <p>Your goal as a mafioso is to eliminate all of the villagers. You will win if the number of villagers equals the number of mafiosi.</p>

  <p>This game's mafiosi are:</p>
  <ul>
    <% @mafiosi.each do |mafioso| %>
      <li><%= mafioso.display_name %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <p>During the night you and the other mafiosi will choose a villager to attack. If you fail to reach a unanimous decision with the other mafiosi on whom to attack your decisions when the last night action has been chosen no one will be attacked.</p>

  <p>Day will begin when the following nighttime actions have completed:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>You and the other mafiosi must choose a villager to attack</li>
    <% if @game.use_detective %>
      <li>The detective will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked the detective will learn the identity of the killers.</li>
    <% end %>
    <% if @game.use_doctor %>
      <li>The doctor will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked that villager will survive the attack.</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <p>Choose your target</p>
  <ul>

    <% @non_mafiosi.filter { |player| player.alive == true }.each do |villager| %>
      <li>
        <% if villager.id != @player_action.target_id %>
          <%= form_with model: @player_action, id: "player_actions#{villager.id}" do |form| %>
            <%= form.hidden_field :player_id, value: @player.id %>
            <%= form.hidden_field :round_id, value: @current_round.id %>
            <%= form.hidden_field :target_id, value: villager.id %>
            <%= form.submit  villager.display_name %>
            <% PlayerAction.where(round_id: @current_round.id, target_id: villager.id, player_id: @mafiosi.select("id")).where.not(player_id: @player.id).select("player_id").each do |mafioso| %>
              (target of <%= @mafiosi.filter { |voter| voter.id == mafioso.player_id }.first.display_name %>)
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <%= villager.display_name %> (Your current target)
          <% PlayerAction.where(round_id: @current_round.id, target_id: villager.id, player_id: @mafiosi.select("id")).where.not(player_id: @player.id).select("player_id").each do |mafioso| %>
            (target of <%= @mafiosi.filter { |voter| voter.id == mafioso.player_id }.first.display_name %>)
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DETECTIVE] %>
  <p>Your goal as a detective is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have may choose a villager to visit. If that villager is attacked you will learn the identity of the Mafiosi.</p>

  <p>Day will begin when the following nighttime actions have completed:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Overnight the Mafiosi are planning which villager to attack.</li>
    <% if @game.use_doctor %>
      <li>The doctor will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked that villager will survive the attack.</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <p>Choose a player to visit:</p>

  <ul>
    <% @game.player.filter { |player| player.alive == true }.each do |villager| %>
      <% if villager.id != @player.id %>
        <li>
          <% if villager.id != @player_action.target_id %>
              <%= form_with model: @player_action, id: "player_actions#{villager.id}" do |form| %>
                <%= form.hidden_field :player_id, value: @player.id %>
                <%= form.hidden_field :round_id, value: @current_round.id %>
                <%= form.hidden_field :target_id, value: villager.id %>
                <%= form.submit  villager.display_name %>
              <% end %>
          <% else %>
            <%= villager.display_name %> (Your current target)
          <% end %>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DOCTOR] %>
  <p>Your goal as a doctor is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have may choose a villager to visit. If that villager is attacked you will prevent that villager from dying.</p>

  <p>Day will begin when the following nighttime actions have completed:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Overnight the Mafiosi are planning which villager to attack.</li>
    <% if @game.use_detective %>
      <li>The detective will visit one of the villagers overnight. If they visit the villager that is attacked the detective will learn the identity of the killers.</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <p>Choose a player to visit:</p>

  <ul>
    <% @game.player.filter { |player| player.alive == true }.each do |villager| %>
      <% if villager.id != @player.id %>
        <% if @player_action == nil or villager.id != @player_action.target_id %>
          <li>
            <%= form_with model: @player_action, id: "player_actions#{villager.id}" do |form| %>
              <%= form.hidden_field :player_id, value: @player.id %>
              <%= form.hidden_field :round_id, value: @current_round.id %>
              <%= form.hidden_field :target_id, value: villager.id %>
              <%= form.submit  villager.display_name %>
            <% end %>
            <%#= form.submit %>
            <%#= link_to villager.display_name, player_path(@player, :action_target => villager.id, :game_redirect => @game.id), data: {turbo_method: :patch} %>
          </li>
<!--          <li>-->
            <%#= link_to villager.display_name, player_path(@player, :action_target => villager.id, :game_redirect => @game.id), data: {turbo_method: :patch} %>
<!--          </li>-->
        <% else %>
          <%= villager.display_name %> (Your current target)
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>